title: Come In With The Rain (Taylor's Version)
description:
Come In With The Rain isn't just a Taylor Swift song.. It's also a saying! Ana doesn't get it, but she tries really hard to use it correctly! Ana, Amy, Nick and Lacey break this song down and add some of their own unconfirmed theories.
What are some phrases that you don't understand? What did we miss? There's lots of ways to contact us!
